data.description: Welcome home to this adorable condo in University Place! Minutes from Chambers Bay, Ruston Point, JBLM, restaurants and shopping! This two bedroom 1.5 bathroom Condo has a patio deck off the formal dining area, individual garage plus two additional parking spaces next to the condo, and Extra storage off the back porch. Come check out this low maintenance condo!     Sprinkler system, landscaping included with HOA dues, New Roof April 2022  Va Assumable! All furniture is negotiable.
